28:16.612 --> 28:20.116
♪ Ten days on the road ♪

28:20.199 --> 28:22.827
♪ Are barely gone ♪

28:24.245 --> 28:28.165
♪ There's a fire
softly burnin' ♪

28:28.249 --> 28:32.294
♪ Supper's on the stove ♪

28:32.378 --> 28:36.048
♪ But it's the light
in your eyes ♪

28:36.132 --> 28:37.633
♪ That makes him warm ♪

28:37.716 --> 28:41.137
-[buzzing]
-[sobbing]

28:41.220 --> 28:47.017
♪ Hey, it's good
to be back home again ♪

28:49.812 --> 28:53.357
